snippet.title: Wheel of Fortune (Sega CD) Playthrough - NintendoComplete
snippet.description:
A complete playthrough of Sony Imagesoft's 1994 Sega CD game, Wheel of Fortune.

This is the Sega CD version of the PC/Windows 3.1 CD game. You can find a video of that version here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EogGjw2bWis
___________
No cheats were used during the recording of this video. 

NintendoComplete (http://www.nintendocomplete.com/) punches you in the face with in-depth reviews, screenshot archives, and music from classic 8-bit NES games!
